This project is built on top of @llm-newsletter-kit/core and serves as both
a production service and a reference implementation for the LLM Newsletter Kit.

===============================================================================

ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT

If you fork this project to build your own newsletter service or create
derivative works based on this code, you must include the following
attribution notice:

  "Powered by LLM Newsletter Kit"

This notice should be included in at least one of the following locations:
- In your newsletter's HTML template footer
- In your service's documentation or website
- In your application's user interface (e.g., footer, about page)

For compliance with Section 4(d) of the Apache License 2.0, this attribution
notice must be retained in derivative works.

