- The heripo logo and associated visual designs
- Domain name: heripo.com

While the source code is freely available under the Apache 2.0 license,
use of these trademarks requires explicit permission from the trademark owner.

If you fork or modify this project for your own use, please:
1. Replace all instances of "heripo" with your own brand name
2. Replace the logo images with your own
3. Update the domain references to your own
4. Update branding in templates and configuration files

Example implementations are welcome to use this code, but should establish
their own brand identity.

For permission to use the "heripo" trademark, contact the project maintainer
via GitHub: https://github.com/kimhongyeon/heripo-research-radar/issues

